


   NPM
   ----
   
   command line tool to get/publish node packages
   
   
   to create package descriptor
   
   > npm init
   
   to get node packages locally as appln dependencies 
   
   > npm i package-name --save
   
   to get node packages locally as dev dependencies 
   
   e.g , build tools , test-case runners , etc...
   
   > npm i package-name --save-dev
   
    to get node packages globally as tools,compilers.etc..
   
   e.g , build tools , test-case runners , etc...
   
   > npm i package-name -g/--global
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   